the electromagnetic field.

00:00:46.675 --> 00:00:50.530
They are quantum states of
the electromagnetic field.

00:00:50.530 --> 00:00:54.250
You A photon, this
particle, is a quantum

00:00:54.250 --> 00:00:55.570
of the electromagnetic field.

00:00:55.570 --> 00:01:00.350
There's a discrete piece of
energy and momentum carried

00:01:00.350 --> 00:01:02.160
