And it had the property
that a acting on alpha

00:02:01.730 --> 00:02:08.889
was equal to alpha--
alpha, the operator a.

00:02:08.889 --> 00:02:10.780
So these were the
coherent states

00:02:10.780 --> 00:02:13.260
we've been talking about.

00:02:13.260 --> 00:02:16.425
And today we're going to
talk about photon states.

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:30.090
So that will be probably
about half of the lecture.

00:02:30.090 --> 00:02:32.050
And in the second
half of the lecture,

00:02:32.050 --> 00:02:39.640
